Text: RE RE Good morning Mike from EliotMike the beginning of next week is pretty light Name a time that is convenient and Ill be there Thanks wrote let me know if you are available one day next week for an interview Thanks Original Message From ENRON mailtoIMCEANOTESeliotlevincsEcom NRONcom Sent Monday June PM To Maggi Mike Subject Good morning Mike from Eliot Mike I hope you had a nice time in Florida Amy and I had a great time with Matty over the weekend He is so cute and was very wellbehaved for us I was just looking at the Enron website again I was reading more about the analyst program which sounds like a great learning opportunity I understand that you may not be able to help me right now as the market is somewhat tight I would definitely appreciate your trying I have attached my resume for you to review or forward to the appropriate personnel I am excited about the opportunity and of course the possibilities Thanks again Mike Eliot Updated Resume doc File Updated Resume doc
